metadata.name: Retro Specs
metadata.description:
SZN2 of The Memes by 6529 has concluded ... so it's time for another retrospective!

This slideshow presents all the memes artwork of SZN2, featuring the following artists:

Cath Simard / k-art / Artur Falcão / Xose Casal / Grant Riven Yun / Cyberh49 / Mindzeye / Oveck / Ben Strauss / 6529er / DirtyRobot / Tyronejkd / Zuphioh / Tjo / Marco Mori / Dangiuz / Killian Moore / FXCKRENDER / DarkMarkArt / VincentVanDough / Brendan North / Neurocolor / Hackatao / Shavonne Wong / Neil Burnell / Che-Yu Wu / TOKYOLUV / Eric Rubens / Muhju / Leafswan / Guido / Arno Kiss / CA CHOU / BertOne / Luna Leonis / Michael Hafftka / Pop Wonder

The music score is excerpted from Verse 1 of the first-ever Open Metaverse piano concert, performed by pandelic.eth.

It's a sequel to the SZN1 retrospective, titled "Auld Lang Syne, 2023" and can be found at —

https:/zora.co/collections/0xeb6218996085c1f31448229c70d1e35f3d0b1d54  
https:/opensea.io/collection/auld-lang-syne-2023

This is the genesis mint from APEX Collective.
